357
00:34:51,672 --> 00:34:53,049
Aku sempat khawatir tadi.

358
00:34:56,594 --> 00:34:57,428
Ini dia tempatnya.

359
00:35:15,571 --> 00:35:16,906
Apa ini?

360
00:35:18,908 --> 00:35:19,742
