480
00:52:31,273 --> 00:52:32,524
Tunggu. Kamera Dua.

481
00:52:34,025 --> 00:52:36,027
- Putar balik itu.
- Baik, Pak.

482
00:52:43,618 --> 00:52:46,246
<font color="#ffff00">MEMINDAI</font>

